<h2>Apple Watch Series 8</h2><br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2023/06/apple-watch-series-8-green.jpg" alt="" width="2500" height="1406" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-901498" /><ul><li><strong>What's the deal?</strong> Take &#36;70 off Apple Watch Series 8</li><br/>
