<div class="center-wrap"><a href="https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHQD1CQ%3Ftag%3Dmacrumors-20%26linkCode%3Dogi%26th%3D1"target="_blank"><div class="fancybutton"><div class="fancybadge">&#36;70 OFF</div>Apple Watch Series 8 (41mm GPS) for &#36;329.00</div></a></div><br/>
<div class="center-wrap"><a href="https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHHLRVQ%3Ftag%3Dmacrumors-20%26th%3D1%26geniuslink%3Dtrue"target="_blank"><div class="fancybutton"><div class="fancybadge">&#36;70 OFF</div>Apple Watch Series 8 (45mm GPS) for &#36;359.00</div></a></div><br/>
<br/>
Lastly, solid deals reappeared on the GPS models of the Apple Watch Series 8 this week, starting at &#36;329.00 for the 41mm and rising to &#36;359.00 for the 45mm. These are both all-time low prices on the Apple Watch Series 8, and they're available in multiple colors and sizes.<br/>
<br/>
