		<description><![CDATA[Apple today introduced the first version of the <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/visionos/">visionOS</a> software, debuting the &zwnj;visionOS&zwnj; 1.0 Developer Beta. The introduction of the beta comes as Apple has announced the launch of the &zwnj;visionOS&zwnj; <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/06/21/apple-vision-pro-sdk/">software development kit</a> (SDK) that will allow third-party developers to build apps for the Vision Pro headset.<br/>
